ww.portlandart.net/archives/2008/04/arts_building_i.html\">PORT\'s story</a> and one tenant\'s account of this <a href=\"http://www.eugeneballetacademy.org/pages/contactus.html\">\"state-of-the-art facility.\"</a>','Philosophy',0,'','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-21','','','2009-05-12 02:59:18','2009-05-12 09:59:18','',2,'http://zoomtopia.com/2-revision-21/',0,'revision','',0),(430,1,'2013-11-04 17:37:43','2013-11-05 00:37:43','http://zoomtopia.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/cropped-Zoomtopia-221.jpg','cropped-Zoomtopia-221.jpg',0,'','inherit','open','open','','cropped-zoomtopia-221-jpg','','','2013-11-04 17:37:43','2013-11-05 00:37:43','',0,'http://zoomtopia.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/cropped-Zoomtopia-221.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(335,1,'2010-03-13 15:09:24','2010-03-13 22:09:24','<a href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/studio7.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-327\" title=\"Creative Studio Space for Lease in Portland\" src=\"http://zoomtopia.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/studio7-300x210.jpg\" alt=\"1000 sq foot Creative Studio Space for Lease in Portland\" width=\"300\" height=\"210\" /></a>\n\nDon\'t miss your chance to lease-to-own studio space in the Eastside of Portland. If you are embarking on a<a title=\"The Current Tenants at Zoomtopia\" href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/community/\">creative enterprise</a>, then this could be your opportunity to <a title=\"Lease-to-Own Philosophy for arts\" href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/about/\">own your studio</a>.\n\n<em>Zoomtopia has one remaining studio space to </em><a title=\"Leasing Info\" href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/leasing/\"><em>lease,</em></a> studio #7, with 1000 square feet for light industrial uses. The remainder of our 10,000 square foot building has been leased, and the tenants include:\n<ul>\n	<li>three dance companies</li>\n	<li>a jeweler</li>\n	<li>an arts quarterly and literary festival</li>\n	<li>a glass blowing studio</li>\n	<li>a photography and multi-media design studio.</li>\n</ul>\nWe have 2000 square feet of common space that is being used for gallery space, lectures and book signings, presentations, and small events.\n\n<strong>This is your chance to join this bustling building, and be a part of the creative community blossoming in the </strong><a href=\"http://www.firstfridayart.com/\"><strong>central eastside arts district</strong></a><strong>.</strong> We are looking forward to the new <a title=\"streetcar plans for eastside on wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portland_Streetcar#Eastside_.28under_construction.29\">Street Car line coming in 2012</a>, and the opportunity to collectively own the building around that same time. We are building a strong, cooperative fellowship of artists, designers, performers, makers and doers, and <strong><a title=\"Contact Zoomtopia about Leasing Space\" href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/contact/\">we want you to join us</a>.</strong>','Lease The Last Remaining Studio or Rehearsal Space at Zoomtopia!',0,'','inherit','open','open','','326-autosave','','','2010-03-13 15:09:24','2010-03-13 22:09:24','',326,'http://zoomtopia.com/326-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(334,1,'2010-03-13 15:05:38','2010-03-13 22:05:38','<a href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/studio7.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-327\" title=\"Creative Studio Space for Lease in Portland\" src=\"http://zoomtopia.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/studio7-300x210.jpg\" alt=\"1000 sq foot Creative Studio Space for Lease in Portland\" width=\"300\" height=\"210\" /></a>\r\n\r\nDon\'t miss your chance to lease-to-own studio space in the Eastside of Portland. If you are embarking on a<a title=\"The Current Tenants at Zoomtopia\" href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/community/\">creative enterprise</a>, then this could be your opportunity to <a title=\"Lease-to-Own Philosophy for arts\" href=\"http://zoomtopia.com/about/\">own your studio</a>.\r\n\r\n<em>Zoomtopia has one remaining stu